---
title: Beef & Bacon Burger with Kumara Wedges for Dinner with Hoisin-Glazed Beef Patties & Sesame Rice for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! Enjoy a beef and bacon burger for dinner, then pack up a rice and veggie mix topped with hoisin beef for lunch the next day. It’s two meals with the effort of just one! Extra delicious!

